# Card-audit puzzle (mtg-948 Part B) backing CLOSED issue mtg-538
# (Card Compatibility: Savannah Lions).
#
# Aspect exercised: a vanilla 2/1 Cat for {W} — it attacks and deals its
# 2 combat damage in real games (the issue's WORKING evidence). No keywords,
# triggers, or activated abilities. P1 is at 4 life with no blockers, so the
# heuristic attacks with the 2/1 and connects for lethal over two turns
# (CR 510.1c combat damage).
#
# HOW TO RUN / VERIFY interactively:
#   mtg tui --start-state test_puzzles/audit_savannah_lions_beatdown.pzl \
#       --p1 heuristic --p2 heuristic --seed 42 -v 2 --no-color-logs
# The log shows "Savannah Lions ... deals 2 damage to Player 1" each turn.

